Class Camera

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nestlabs.sdk.Device
      • com.nestlabs.sdk.Camera
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable

    public class Camera
extends Device
implements Parcelable
    Camera represents a single Nest Camera device. It contains all information associated with a Camera device.
